      <title>能源价格上涨对企业造成损害，新西兰采取紧急行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/nz-takes-urgent-action-as-soaring-energy-prices-hurt-businesses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰政府公布了一系列能源和电力领域的改革措施，以应对批发电力成本的飙升，这导致一些大型制造商重新审视其业务的未来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/nz-takes-urgent-action-as-soaring-energy-prices-hurt-businesses</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 04:29:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
